Proximity
+ 1 hour from Tampa & Clearwater
+ 1.5 hrs from Clermont
+ 2hrs from Orlando
+ 2hrs from Sarasota
Directions
Coming from Spring Hill:
Take US 19 South. After the light at Little, turn right onto Phelps Rd and stay right onto Race Track Rd.
Coming from New Port Richey:
Take US 19 North. After the light at Denton, turn left onto Phelps Rd and stay right onto Race Track Rd.
Coming from Tampa:
Take 589 Veterans Pkwy North. Take 52 West, then turn right onto US 19 North. After the light at Denton, turn left onto Phelps Rd and stay right onto Race Track Rd.
